translate ru SarahBelmontFollowup_9ab17346:
    # "Sarah had found herself with a rare free day. No chores, no tasks, no training."
    ""

translate ru SarahBelmontFollowup_6fba8290:
    # "She decided to use her free day to explore Lethram."
    ""

translate ru SarahBelmontFollowup_e624a658:
    # "Ever since she had arrived, she had mostly been confined to the mercenary camp."
    ""

translate ru SarahBelmontFollowup_566a4444:
    # "Lethram was one of the greatest cities on the planet, so Sarah reasoned, it would be a shame not to explore it a little, while she was still here."
    ""

translate ru SarahBelmontFollowup_efd1b18c:
    # "She wandered through the shopping district. Even after having been in Lethram for a while, Sarah could still find herself stunned by the sights."
    ""

translate ru SarahBelmontFollowup_d2d7b896:
    # "Strange orbs, gemstones, trinkets, entire shops filled with things she had never before seen in her life."
    ""

translate ru SarahBelmontFollowup_10fdfb73:
    # "She made her way from shop to shop, slowly winding down the street of the shop district, leading into the harbor."
    ""

translate ru SarahBelmontFollowup_6fa159b5:
    # "This was the real heart of Lethram, it’s world famous harbor."
    ""

translate ru SarahBelmontFollowup_80ba7805:
    # "Looking out over a railing, she could overlook the docks, seeing the countless people moving in some chaotic yet organized mess."
    ""

translate ru SarahBelmontFollowup_1f5eb739:
    # "Sailors, merchants, soldiers, dock officials, people from strange lands. The sight almost overwhelmed her."
    ""

translate ru SarahBelmontFollowup_d51e105c:
    # "But Sarah wandered into the crowd, pushing her way through, becoming part of it. This was what it meant to really experience Lethram."
    ""

translate ru SarahBelmontFollowup_d0fa6319:
    # "Walking past some of the harbor stalls, Sarah suddenly heard a familiar voice call out."
    ""

translate ru SarahBelmontFollowup_469bcdf8:
    # cb "Hey there blondie."
    cb ""

translate ru SarahBelmontFollowup_4ba4858c:
    # "Sarah turned her head towards the voice and saw captain Belmont, standing on the upper deck of his ship, waving at her."
    ""

translate ru SarahBelmontFollowup_414d4f80:
    # "She instantly turned her head away again, ignoring the vile man. She pretended to continue shopping."
    ""

translate ru SarahBelmontFollowup_68c5580d:
    # cb "Come on, blondie, I know you heard me."
    cb ""

translate ru SarahBelmontFollowup_d12d1809:
    # "Captain Belmont continued to pester her from aboard his ship."
    ""

